These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, analyst, journalist, teacher, videographer, nurse, musician
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, lily, rose, poppy, daffodil, orchid
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, motorbike, scooter, skateboard, trike, van
 1. the designer is on the left of the musician##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 3. the person driving the bike is the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the teacher##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the nurse is in the middle##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growslily##1
15. the person driving the van is on the left of the designer##1
16. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
17. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
19. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
20. the person who growsrose is on the left of the analyst##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Job      | journalist    | designer     | musician  | nurse   | teacher | videographer      | analyst          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| Flower         | tulip | aconite | poppy | daffodil | lily   | rose     | orchid |
| Transport     | van      | trike   | bike   | motorbike  | scooter  | skateboard | jet-ski       |

