.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-2::.
7 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, domino, snooker, poker, canasta, bridge
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, comedy, fantasy, martial-arts, romance, sports
There are 7 different favourite colors: green, red, ivory, purple, emerald, orange, apricot
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, ship, subway, taxi, train
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is the person who likes red##1
 4. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is the person playing domino##1
10. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
12. the person who likes orange is the person driving the ship##1
13. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
14. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
15. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
16. the person who likes orange is the person driving the ship##1
17. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
18. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
19. the person driving the subway is the person watching comedy movies##1
20. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4      |      5       |       6       |     7      |
