There 7 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, grapefruit, grapes, nectarine, peas, zucchini
House: farmhouse, futuristic, townhouse, art-deco, palace, modern, cottage
The people have 7 different jobs:  paramedic, engineer, musician, designer, dancer, teacher, coach
 1. the person drinking juice is the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the art-deco house is on the left of the modern house##1
 4. the futuristic house is the designer##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is the teacher##1
 6. the musician is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the right of the dancer##1
10. the engineer is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person eating zucchini is the musician##1
12. the person eating cranberry is the dancer##1
13. the coach is on the left of the art-deco house##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the modern house##1
15. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
16. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is the musician##1
18. the palace house is on the far right##1
19. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
20. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
21. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2      |      3      |       4       |     5     |    6    |    7     |
